\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 That - oh when I was - started working. Oh aye. Oh it wasna afore - never - like afore}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7291225\charrsid9768143 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 hand. In fact I'm going - in Plainstones you ken, thei
r clothe, are - you ken, wee frocks and things was cheap but in my more mature life - I didna ken but - you know like to get - ken I didna fancy other folk and wearing them - or cut down to me or owt like that, I just be ken - you know, just to ken if I s
t
arted working or not, and it wasnae the - as I tell you the money we'd to hand it in. But a half crown maybe. And it took me a bit of saving up a half crown a week, to get what I wanted. Of course I'd get the material in the mill. And then I had to have i
t - aye, it was cheaper and that, and - then - I would save up again - for - to pay for - for the making of it. Oh never - ken like waste it or owt like that for another.
