id it for a while. And then he just - because - I can mind and that that he - he called them last - a last. And there were three sizes of the feet like, you ken, what I would take and that. And he used to and that, and then he stopped. Of course he could 
have got a wee pair of shoes at one and eleven}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7291225\charrsid9768143  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 
pence ha'penny then and - fancy ken like I mean but then leather he could have went away and got three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7291225\charrsid9768143 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 pence}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
