o
 be there. And Johnny Marshall, he was manager of Mc George's factory, in fact Lizzie Marshall and that like, his daughter - married Mr James, and she lives about Cardoness Street Lizze. She married the boss's son. But Mr - Johnny Marshall, like we're jus
