Oh no, it was - my own man - my - Bob was - of course like Bob's father and - even his brother Jock over there, they were all you ken like - they just join I think joined it after another like and so forth. Oh no, my father - but I'll tell you what I thin
k
. A - a communist is it - ken, them kind that argue and bitter, I think he was - something to do with - that, but - but another word, ken, down at - at the Dockhead and that, used to be, ken - they used to have ken on a - on a - platform, and lay it off l
ike and - and that, it was something like that. I dinna ken if you'd have called a Comm - Communist or - or - that wasnae the word like - they used about him - like agitators. Ken, they were just a crowd of ag - agitating.
