Well - it wasnae Greyfriars, but I used to go to the - Band - Band of Hope every Monday night, and I'll tell you it was South Free. And that's the church away at the bottom of the High Street. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 That's where you turn right?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 That's righ
t. And the - the Hall, as I call this place, we cut through into Burns Street, it was - that - that's the name it got, Mill Hole, I dinna know where they got the idea, Mill Hole, and the hall was there, we went to the Band of Hope, every Monday night a cr
owd of us again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 What did they do there?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 
Oh just singing and - ken, maybe - a man talking about - the Bible and - you ken, all them wee things. In fact this - Jardine was - a - a great - ken, South Free, ken, some of the churches, some of the li
kes of - say the - our church, and McAllister - put us - I think the same as - tattie merchants, they used to be. Well I think they - this McAllister and they're great Greyfriars, ken, you'd have said, oh well, they're well in with the church and that. Th
e
 Jardines were the very same, but I'm no - meaning - the old Jardine, but Tommy Jardine like, and the other brother and that, the undertakers like and that, well their sons - are what you called - from this old Mr Jardine, but he was awfully good like. It
 was him, ken just what you would say now youth clubs, they talk about youth clubs, well - I think it's just something like that. Keeping you all together and one thing and another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Keeping you off the streets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 And keeping you off the street. And
 I think and that it - it - it was far nicer the likes that and - and you were amongst you ken and - and mixing. Now - in fact they say and that there's nothing for - there's nothing for young ones.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 What about the rest of Sunday, were you allowed out to play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 You'd to keep the - Sabbath holy. Oh nae - no - you didna get skipping and carrying on, oh no, not -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Were you allowed to play games in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Well I could - I used to - be the, ken, the ringleader in that way, ken like - maybe
 saying - oh, maybe playing hide and seek or anything. But there you were and that, and maybe getting into a place and werenae - and then of course, the door had always to open whenever you heard it, my father. And you had to come out of the hiding place 
and then he'd say, oh spy, and the he was - what - what was ken going on, what was going on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 So he was quite strict about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Oh he was - oh -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 And yet he didn't go to the church himself you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Never - not even for Communion. He never even went - took Communion that - I can mind of.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Was he a member?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 
Yes. Yes. And he used to have his Communion card and that and - if you'd have liked to try and slipped it in, now fancy a - a thing like that, fancy, ken, you're no there and try
ing to - pass - just like a - a fogged note or anything like that, pass it. He never, no, he never and that, I - in fact he's lucky I think that - the likes of - the minister did - ken, bury him, because in - I ken - in our church and that, it used to be,
 I don't know now, but - miss three Communions, you're stroked off the roll. You're right off the roll. And he was on that, and I think it was just with my ma and that, well ken - as I tell you, she was good living, and maybe that's the reason.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Did she manage to go regularly every Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 
Aye well - more maybe - night time, ken there were three services. The morning, afternoon and night time, and I've seen my ma but - I'll tell you what she was a great for - like - the Salvation Army. And it was 
just - my ma liked the Salvation Army. And you ken, with - women she ran about with and that, and they used to have a - you ken, meetings in the aft - like a - maybe meeting in a - Monday afternoon, and all meet like, and have a wee cup of tea, in the hal
l, if there were anything special on, my ma like this - she - she really liked the Salvation Army. And - and always - she said it was always ken homely and they were that nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Were you ever in the choir or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Me? Oh no, I never was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Did you ever say grace at meals in your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 
There - oh there were never much - of that. It was just a case of, sit down and - you get up again and - whoever liked to wash the dishes get at it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 What about when you went to bed at night, did anybody teach you to say your prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 
No, only my ma, you ken, my ma was just to say ken, now, mind say your prayers you ken and that was one thing about her. But - my father never - never mentioned, ken, anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Did your mother teach you any or did she just sort of leave you to your own devises?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Oh it was more ken of Our Father but - I mean, even before I went to school, but then at the school you learnt you ken all. And you get -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 You would be taught some of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Yes.
 That's what I often say and that on there, when you hear and that and you hear ministers too - and the - the Lord's Prayer like and I often think on that too. It used to - which art in Heaven, and it - now it's - who art in Heaven.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 You were taught which at the school were you?
