rough that, and it used to madden me and I would say, oh nothing of the kind and that - we - we were - ken, we were all the same and I - you ken, I wouldna have nothing said about ever you ken and that that's one thing we - I'll no have anything said abou
t a body. I - I was just as I think of myself. But I couldna say like and that or - or - ken - ken so - even at the present day and that, or going away and telling on you or - or -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13396319\charrsid9768143 
 clipping as we call it, a clip}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 . There were nothing worse as a clipe. But I c
