ht. I says - I'm no - going behind the bush. Oh she says, nothing of the kind. I says, aye, well, it is so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 How about the teachers, did you like any of the teachers specially?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Oh well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Or were there any that you didn't get on with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 O
h there were only - one - teacher, I think it was the fifth class he was in, or the sixth. This - we called him Tommy Maxwell you ken, Mr Maxwell like but - we got his first name, Tommy and that. But anyway he came from Troqueer Road. And - he was awfully
 strict, you ken what I mean. Well I - ken, I mean, we never thought anything about it and that but because the simple reason that we just - do as your telled kind of style and that. But he was really - ken, inclined to be a wee bit stricter.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 What sort of things was he fussy about then?
