Ah well, see the likes of history. Tommy - ken, you'd to put your mind and - ken, attend to that subject like, history. He was a great one for that. And then Mr - ken, say - Mr Duncan like - and that, this - the la
st the ex sixth and that of course, it was just a case of - everything was put in with him, just a mixture like you know, all that we got like and that, that's what I say now when I think you ken - Linda'll say to me - what did you get at the school grann
y? And I just tell her straight. I say, well I just am telling you Linda, that's all that I got.
