e
r about that, and the other ones - Commercial like. As I said - I was cooking and laundry and - all that carry on. And it was really - it was grand and that, I can always mind the - teacher that had our - there too, she was a Miss Crichton. And she was re
ally -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Was that the domestic science mistress?
\par 
