Science, yes. Aye, she was just ken a wee body like myself and that but - oh, it was - smashing like and that there. Oh I enjoyed every minute up there too like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Did you still do English and arithmetic and things like that at the High school?
