lled it. And then - maybe Thursday afternoon it would be - cooking. 'Course you'd to take your own stuff and that too for to - and baking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 But you still had to do other lessons too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 And you had - aye, yes. But I mean that did really take a lot o
f our time up like and that. We were learning anyway but still we'd other - subjects to take for all that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 How did you like the teachers at the high school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Well to tell you the truth and that I canna - I often think and that they were all just kind of the same you ken like. I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 All just teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 
Well - Nessie of course, that's - another thing, she'll say to me too, oh, ken - you've to respect - you've to respect - even a boss, you've to - you must - and I - ken what I mean,
 fair mad with me, no like you know, they'll no listen, they just - out and say - oh she gets mad at me. And she'll say - oh I wish to goodness woman that you'd - cut this - respecting, respecting, she says, why should you humble yourself, or even take - 
n
o - or humble to a boss? I says, look here, in my days, I says, to get a job - for all that you were making, you had to respect - and there were nae - carrying on like young ones - as I heard - I - a young one in a shop. And do you know what she turned ar
o
und and said to the boss? Oh - and I believe it and that because I simply - as I telled you up in that school with the drawings, it was terrible. Ken what she said to the - he said, ken attend - attend to the - like they were waiting to get served, and th
e - the boss says to -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Did the teachers use the strap a lot then?
