\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 But you quite enjoyed working in the factory?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 At - at the factory I was far better, yet I liked the - you ken, lassies and that and one thing and another, and then the weave
rs - not that - I'm meaning that - with rage or anything, but they were all, ken, all like - they were all old women like and that we called them, but - no, irrespective of that like I got on with them all. But it's just that I hadna the heart for that, i
t - oh I - I nearly broke my heart all the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 How long did you stay in McGeorge's?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Oh - I don't - I was barely a year in it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 How long were you with Wyllies before you went there, from leaving the school? Was it just a short time too?
