w said like, I opened the door and shouted in like, he says, would you - would you mind taking this parcel - for Mrs Leithie you ken up the stair? So I says - I often say and that that long ago - that - I mean, when I think on my own mother and - them all
 
and that, heavens it was different altogether, you never - some folk'll say, oh it couldna have been and that, there must have been fighting, there must have been badness and all this and that, well I canna mind nothing like that. And I never - no, and I'
