n, never meant anything by it but - Bob used to this wee bloke, and - I'm wee - and - and - you ken he brought the heavens down - for me that - boy you ken at the time. And ken after I started going with Bob you ken, and whenever we met him - and ken - Bo
b
 would say to me - he says, look. Have a look at him. He says, that's what you were going out with - that's who you - and you ken I used to - and I was fair - aye, even with him, I was going - I says, oh away and take a jump and - and leave him alone, I l
