g, it was then, you ken what I mean. In fact it was himself you ken, he would say, you ken, he said to me too, he says, well mind he says, Jen, I'm no - he says - say, ken, we had our nights. Monday, Wednesday, Friday and a Saturday night and a Sunday. An
d
 the other two nights. I hope you're no - do you ken - I hope you're no out you ken with your buddies, that's what he called them. I hope you're no out with your buddies and that, you ken what I mean. And I would say, oh no, but many a night - ken, I did 
go out for a daft night with them you ken. The Tuesday or the Thursday, I did go out like and that. But - there were - you ken there were nae harm in it and that but he thought maybe I was sitting in the house and that.
