o on, got - like nowadays, they just ken and they're married. But you had to go on for a certain length of time before you ever thought, as I tell you, my father wanae on, the thought I was rather young, and I'm sure Bob and that, and I was ken tig towing
 like long afore I ken went out regular with him. Tig towing because the f}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14711763\charrsid9768143 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 
