d, in the close and - talking and that and here - it was then he said, oh Jenny, he says, I want you he says - to meet my mother and father and - ken and that. Well, I kenned like his two sisters, I kenned Nen and Jean like. In fact wee Jean and that - hi
s
 - youngest sister like - she a hanging eye after a brother of mine. Wee Jean Robson and - and - our Davie, but Jean was, ken, and many a time my ma used to - it was funny, she passed that remark, she says, ay, she says, I would like to ken see Davie gett
ing wee Jean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 But it didn't happen?
