ough man like, I'm no saying anything about Rob like, a good enough man and that, but it just shows you and that how - you just feel like that couple, you ken. And wee Jean Robson, she was an awfully - in fact she - she's - I think she's oftener - oftener
 down by - like just her nerves and - like and that, and wee Jean's having an awful time of it like.
