hat I mean, they were inclined to you like with teachers you ken and that and just as much as you ken but anyway - I never - it never appealed to me that way and that. I liked - every teacher I had. And - bar that, with the headmaster giving me that strap
,
 and I never - by God Jen, watched and that. I never got a strap again from the man. Anyway I didna ken he was deaf. But - there's some of them and that, you know, one or two ken were inclined to be you ken with teachers and it wasna - you ken what I mean
.
 They liked to chat back to them. I mind there were a boy and he - my - like he went through in school with me, and he was - but I don't know really what you ken and that, and this teacher and that - in fact it was Miss Caldow that - asked me - if I'd go 
