 it, I - I - you ken, I thought it was terrible. He was - he was in the front seat and I was about ken the middle, I wasnae at the top of the class, I was about the middle. And I just thought like and that - and it was funny, Miss Faldow and that said to 
m
e - ken, when I was over - and - I washed the steps - on the Wednesday night, the front ones. Well on Saturday - I washed ken them at the back. And I got - you ken, threepence for the front ones and threepence for the back, that was sixpence. But - awfull
y good like, ken with clothes or anything like that, no that they were any used to me, but clothes and -
