 that and so forth, but oh mercy, they were - they were nae difference from me - as what - ken, with her own daughter. And Mrs Caldow and that, she was awfully - ken, she was really - never grudged doing anything - for that woman. And believe me - I wasna
 that long left the school - and if I'd have got my way like and that, I would have went down to London.
