\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Do you remember anyone ever being described as a real gentleman?
