No, to tell you the God's truth and that, I - I - I canna even - think you ken on that - with just the - the - the - really the way we go on - I - I - fighting or anything 
like that I mean there were never - we never had this, ken like - no like what - nowadays - never seemed to you ken like - had any cause to fight, you ken like say we were all together and that in that, never any cause.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 You got on quite well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1604703 JR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 We just all go on, I cannae ever mind of fighting with any of my - mates.
