- America, married a Swiss, now her poor old mother - in the gardens, and mind that was you ken you would have said, oh that's - you ken, some of the folk would say, oh, ken, oh you ken, what a - what to come down to you ken and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8206157 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid921314\charrsid9768143 Do you think some of
